Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.74,0:02:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, just a few more.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.12,0:02:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we're far enough from the Inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.13,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry, so we can return.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.29,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's very clean.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.67,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost as if...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear that sound?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? We didn't notice anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I do feel a presence.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.28,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There may be a survivor.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it's an Outsider?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it's a cursed being of the Inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A cursed being will spread \Nthe curse to another.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We mustn't let anyone escape!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.79,0:04:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't kill all who are suspicious, \Nthere's no point!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.05,0:04:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one in charge of this unit. \NI'll go look!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.48,0:04:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,! knew it, someone's there.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.48,0:04:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is someone there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're there, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.03,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move from there! \NI'm from the military!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! You're safe now.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.93,0:05:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize it's difficult \Nto walk in the dark,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.98,0:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but the sun will rise soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hurt your leg?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, then take your time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That lamp...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.71,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've brought it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be very forgetful.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. What is your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.89,0:06:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, why were you sleeping \Nin such a place?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.82,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was sleeping at home \Nwith my aunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.00,0:07:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be forgetful too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,have horns.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A tail too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an Outsider.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do you curse people?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.73,0:07:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not spread the curse. \NI am different than the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.95,0:07:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten my name.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I have no name.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.70,0:07:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we close?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.41,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.41,0:07:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your home.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.54,0:07:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you'll see it soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.08,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.09,0:07:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait one moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot touch you even if your leg hurts,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.47,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can hang onto this.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.89,0:08:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.39,0:08:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just thought it was \Na weird way to use this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.19,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.59,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrap it with this last.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.31,0:08:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, try not to wrap it too tight.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.19,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, aren't you afraid of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.99,0:08:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of my appearance.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.08,0:09:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My appearance doesn't affect you at all?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, you look different than me, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.84,0:09:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. Are you afraid of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.59,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.01,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you live by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.32,0:09:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.20,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, more like I drop by every so often \Nrather than live here.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where your house is?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.85,0:10:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.73,0:10:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You injury isn't serious,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.61,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you'd like, you can rest here.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.61,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's slightly dirty, \Nbut there is a bed in the back room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.66,0:10:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your bed, isn't it? I'd feel bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.87,0:10:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am cursed, so I do not sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.75,0:10:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain, warmth...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.88,0:10:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've forgotten many things.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! You know lots, \Nso I'll call you Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.44,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, call me whatever you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for your house \Nafter your leg heals.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return tomorrow morning \Nwith some food.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.08,0:11:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I have only berries today, \Nbut please stay to rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.50,0:11:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.51,0:11:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going somewhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.38,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.30,0:11:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.85,0:11:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, this area is safe \Nas long as you don't leave the house.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.81,0:11:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go too far either.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.39,0:11:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll walk you to the front door!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.66,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.08,0:11:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, I apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to bed already?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.79,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need help?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.09,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Then I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.49,0:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Must hurry...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.53,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.45,0:13:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If all aren't...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.60,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.13,0:14:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.23,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she have...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.90,0:14:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,left the house?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.41,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,/ see. She must have been frightened.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she ran away.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't with this appearance?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.42,0:14:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, what would I do \Nsaving this child...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva!I
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.51,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, where have you been?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to not leave the house!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.52,0:15:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Here!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was making this \Nas a thank you gift for yesterday!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.40,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, crouch down!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But it's dangerous to touch me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.95,0:15:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if I don't touch you, right? \NJust crouch down.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.33,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.21,0:15:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.26,0:15:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.02,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it looks great on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.44,0:15:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's start by cleaning up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.05,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick up the heavy objects, \Nso please clean up the dust and trash.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.59,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.27,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, once you're done with that, \Ncan you clean this shelf too?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.04,0:16:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, I'll carry these items to my room, \Nso please leave them as they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.96,0:16:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to help you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They might get mixed up, \Nso I'll carry them on my own...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.76,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...80 I thought it was a giant strawberry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That must've been very big.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, we'll just wrap the bandages \Nand we're done.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.06,0:17:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Thank you, Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.11,0:17:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.15,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.07,0:17:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.32,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Teacher, \Nthere's something I want to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.74,0:17:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really fluffy and sweet, \Nand there's lots of sugar...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize. It was rather difficult.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.43,0:17:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just never seen a pancake \Nthat was this black, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.22,0:17:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eat only what looks edible.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the burnt parts are tasty too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.31,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The burnt parts aren't good for your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just eat a little.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a new curtain?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.86,0:17:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since I found another one \Nwith the perfect size.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this should be good.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, it's ready!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine! \NI've had it many times before!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.69,0:18:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But with some sugar in it, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I feel like \NI can drink it today!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful not to burn yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.12,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.58,0:18:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bitter.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, did you find the sugar?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.05,0:19:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but I think there's some here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.27,0:19:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of books here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.52,0:19:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See if you can find anything you like.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the sugar too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.11,0:19:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I eat one?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.68,0:19:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So sweet!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.56,0:19:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Teacher, let's play hide-and-seek!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.02,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I just count to ten?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.49,0:20:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, a hundred!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred then. All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.83,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.88,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Six.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.72,0:20:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Seven.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.63,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.47,0:20:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eleven.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.43,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirteen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.15,0:20:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourteen.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.65,0:20:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.28,0:20:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In a place like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now ls my chance...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.50,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,ll wonder where Teacher is?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.09,0:21:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.31,0:21:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello! Are you playing hide-and-seek too?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.90,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.74,0:21:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to take it back?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.08,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.92,0:21:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going \Nto keep that soul all to yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.76,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soul?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:47.43,0:21:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to hurry and return that soul \Nto Mother while its still pure.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.23,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.73,0:22:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,About that soul you are with.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do to Shiva?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.19,0:22:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.86,0:22:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So you give names to souls.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.86,0:22:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.41,0:22:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We all know.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.75,0:22:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What you all call the curse.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.75,0:22:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,you know how to break the curse?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.88,0:22:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How to break the curse?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.88,0:22:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know anything, do you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.30,0:22:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'm not the same as all of you \Nthat spread the curse around!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.81,0:22:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose child are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.40,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whose child"?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.11,0:22:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,lam human!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.90,0:22:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me your name.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:47.65,0:22:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:49.41,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans have one, don't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:56.87,0:22:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,lam...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really from the Inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:01.29,0:23:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the same as us, a dark child?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:05.17,0:23:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Leave this place at once!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.30,0:23:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Which are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,lam...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.83,0:23:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.00,0:23:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.05,0:23:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.43,0:23:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I was good at hiding?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:59.39,0:24:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:01.73,0:24:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find your book?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:03.31,0:24:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.03,0:24:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.65,0:24:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.45,0:24:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll choose this one!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.21,0:24:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,/ must at least protect her...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.80,0:24:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so that she doesn't get cursed.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.34,0:24:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as she isn't cursed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:38.89,0:24:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that one day...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:43.69,0:24:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"The god who was punished...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:46.77,0:24:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,had everything taken away...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.82,0:24:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and was turned into a hideous creature."
Dialogue: 10,0:24:55.99,0:24:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we continue the rest next time?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:58.87,0:24:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:01.37,0:25:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.84,0:25:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.75,0:25:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:14.47,0:25:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No! This is precious to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:18.39,0:25:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.98,0:25:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:27.06,0:25:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.44,0:25:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.41,0:25:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these your friends?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.29,0:25:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My family.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:45.12,0:25:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.84,0:25:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, how did you become an Outsider?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:57.18,0:25:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't everyone else with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.22,0:26:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to tell me?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:05.27,0:26:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.64,0:26:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.02,0:26:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a human, who lived in the Inside,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:13.82,0:26:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had a wife and child.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.90,0:26:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have been living \Nan ordinary life.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:20.91,0:26:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cannot remember \Nmy voice or appearance.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:25.58,0:26:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my name or my face...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.38,0:26:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure... \Nif anything is real or not.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:37.09,0:26:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.68,0:26:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to stay connected with those, \Nso I've been holding onto it,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.06,0:26:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe I no longer need it.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:51.73,0:26:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.40,0:26:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay if you can't remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.69,0:26:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if things have changed...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:00.53,0:27:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,please stay beside them, Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:03.37,0:27:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's more important \Nthan remembering.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:17.71,0:27:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to though?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:20.72,0:27:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.76,0:27:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:26.27,0:27:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been cursed.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.03,0:27:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:38.74,0:27:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.65,0:27:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.90,0:27:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. What were you saying?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:44.62,0:27:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.74,0:27:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:50.50,0:27:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.12,0:27:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've talked a little too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.09,0:27:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We walked lots today, \Nso you must be tired.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep well.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:03.01,0:28:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Good night, Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.31,0:28:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:21.84,0:29:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:23.26,0:29:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.18,0:29:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? No...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:33.02,0:29:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, please...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.69,0:29:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.65,0:29:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.35,0:30:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.94,0:30:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's pancake is nicely baked and tasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.95,0:30:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I'm glad you like it.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.49,0:30:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, will you pass the sugar?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.58,0:30:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.54,0:30:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:42.04,0:30:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:43.25,0:30:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:46.13,0:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The sugar...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.92,0:30:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.47,0:30:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:58.27,0:31:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva... would you like to go somewhere far?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:04.78,0:31:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere far? Where?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:07.99,0:31:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have \Na specific place in mind, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:15.04,0:31:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That sounds really fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:22.00,0:31:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go after I eat this! \NI'll be done soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:25.92,0:31:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it may take a couple of days,
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.97,0:31:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's fully prepare \Nand set out tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:34.72,0:31:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, will you pack up \Neverything you need as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:39.23,0:31:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.73,0:31:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:52.41,0:31:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:02.50,0:32:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:04.38,0:32:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:06.88,0:32:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:08.88,0:32:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:10.72,0:32:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.47,0:32:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:15.68,0:32:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:19.72,0:32:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:21.73,0:32:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 10,0:32:31.70,0:32:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.86,0:32:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:36.24,0:32:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd need to clean this up \Nbefore we can set out.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.75,0:32:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:45.67,0:32:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:50.76,0:32:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night then, Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:53.55,0:32:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, good night, Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.44,0:33:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's a small village...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.73,0:33:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,where humans live...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:14.61,0:33:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:16.70,0:33:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that's... what's best for her...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:44.06,0:33:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:47.06,0:33:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, are you ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:50.94,0:33:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute! I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:17.47,0:34:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:19.59,0:34:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:49.83,0:34:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It should be much safer this way \Nthan continuing to stay with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:34:55.67,0:34:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can find a village with people,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:58.17,0:35:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure someone generous will help Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:04.01,0:35:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid this is the best option I have.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:10.23,0:35:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just beyond here,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:12.48,0:35:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}if there's a child close to her age, \NI'm sure she won't grow bored either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:35:18.15,0:35:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll have better food foo.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:21.41,0:35:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For Shiva, I must...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:24.99,0:35:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I must... save her.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:31.25,0:35:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,While I still have the time.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:36.42,0:35:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the least I could do.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:57.07,0:35:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:58.36,0:35:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:00.15,0:36:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seemed different.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.49,0:36:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to spill out.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:06.53,0:36:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nearly empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:08.87,0:36:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.66,0:36:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't know about Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:14.04,0:36:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:15.92,0:36:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it knows.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:17.92,0:36:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nearly empty.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:35.40,0:36:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're concerned about that one.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:41.99,0:36:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that one will end its duty soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:46.74,0:36:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We won't be able to return it \Nto Mother like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:50.37,0:36:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just return the shell.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:03.63,0:37:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:05.51,0:37:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I was expecting to walk more...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:14.10,0:37:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look around first.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:22.78,0:37:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like this place is a farm. \NEven their equipment is left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:30.87,0:37:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here would be...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:39.25,0:37:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shiva! Don't go too far!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:46.26,0:37:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,/ didn't realize \Nhow much I was pushing her.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:52.02,0:37:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:54.43,0:37:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:08.91,0:38:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, come over here! \NThere's lots of rare flowers!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.12,0:38:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, I want to check the houses, \Nso will you wait here?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:19.50,0:38:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I want you here with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:22.30,0:38:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I finish, let's look together.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:24.59,0:38:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:43.11,0:38:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:33.74,0:39:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,/ see...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:35.95,0:39:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This village foo... is now...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:46.92,0:39:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we must try the village up ahead...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:52.22,0:39:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:00.44,0:40:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,ls that...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:02.40,0:40:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a villager?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:09.94,0:40:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:11.49,0:40:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva!I
Dialogue: 10,0:40:19.37,0:40:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Must save...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:21.37,0:40:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, run!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:23.88,0:40:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I must...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:26.88,0:40:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva!I
Dialogue: 10,0:40:28.38,0:40:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Save...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:58.16,0:41:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:01.16,0:41:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:04.37,0:41:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:16.80,0:41:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Then these are all the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:22.60,0:41:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where everyone went.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:25.31,0:41:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting separated, \Nthey all stayed together.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:32.86,0:41:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:34.61,0:41:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, you lie down too.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:37.41,0:41:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:38.87,0:41:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it, please?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:51.34,0:41:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Teacher, please listen like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:56.38,0:42:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, before I met you, I woke up once.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:00.60,0:42:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all alone and it was dark.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:03.22,0:42:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I thought that I might not be able to \Nreturn to my village anymore,
Dialogue: 10,0:42:07.85,0:42:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,my body couldn't move.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:10.57,0:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I was scared, so I closed my eyes, \Nwishing for someone to come.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:15.49,0:42:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I woke up again, \Nyou were there, Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:20.53,0:42:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as [ thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.70,0:42:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, it may be difficult \Nto return to your village,
Dialogue: 10,0:42:28.17,0:42:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but surely to the Inside...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:30.88,0:42:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:32.80,0:42:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:35.72,0:42:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?! Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:39.72,0:42:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:43.97,0:42:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Teacher, I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:47.10,0:42:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:48.64,0:42:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:50.56,0:42:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's before I even met you. \NMuch earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:43:07.79,0:43:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:23.10,0:43:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we spending the night here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:25.72,0:43:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, since the sun has set already \Nand the weather isn't looking good.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:31.40,0:43:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rest here.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:33.36,0:43:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just brush away the dust, \Nthis place isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:49.54,0:43:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:51.87,0:43:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't put it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:59.42,0:44:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.38,0:44:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:43.89,0:44:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it at this hour?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:47.01,0:44:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm glad you noticed.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:49.35,0:44:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was returning to the village up ahead, \Nbut I came over after I saw your light.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:55.65,0:44:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How 'bout it? Won't you leave this place \Nand move to the Inside?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:59.19,0:45:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our village received \Npermission from the king.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:02.74,0:45:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, we appreciate your kindness, \Nbut we're fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:06.66,0:45:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, no soldiers have come yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:09.41,0:45:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come with us as a villager.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:12.08,0:45:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can even come to my house first. \NAfter finding out about Shiva's curse...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:14.29,0:45:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you can even come to my house first.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:14.50,0:45:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're holding back, \Nthere's no need for it! Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:15.54,0:45:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're holding back, \Nthere's no need for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:17.88,0:45:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine, just go!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:19.38,0:45:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right. I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:21.59,0:45:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to overstep, but my village \Nis down the road to the west.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:26.05,0:45:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two houses \Nlined up in the very back.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:28.80,0:45:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My house is with a dog in the entrance.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:32.18,0:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our departure is tomorrow at noon.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:34.94,0:45:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you change your mind, \Ncome visit us.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:43.69,0:45:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there anything I could do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:45:48.82,0:45:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,ls she going to experience \Nthe same loneliness of being cursed?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:54.50,0:45:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:56.96,0:46:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even knowing the traces \Nof what I was looking for...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:03.17,0:46:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Life, time...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:08.22,0:46:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,/ was left behind from everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:17.81,0:46:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She will also have to face this pain...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:46:31.03,0:46:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is even left of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:38.75,0:46:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What could /...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:46.38,0:46:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I do for Shiva?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:53.47,0:46:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A soul...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:59.60,0:47:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If only I had a soul...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:28.97,0:47:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just attack from behind...
Dialogue: 10,0:47:31.09,0:47:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,/ have no choice. This is the only way...
Dialogue: 10,0:47:38.93,0:47:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, would that child wish \Nfor something like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:45.19,0:47:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I thinking? This is as if...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:47:50.20,0:47:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,!/ must return.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:51.82,0:47:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 10,0:47:53.07,0:47:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Drat!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:55.66,0:47:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You... monster!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:58.16,0:48:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Stop! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:00.66,0:48:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Run! It's an Outsider! Run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:01.79,0:48:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:03.92,0:48:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:05.00,0:48:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:11.51,0:48:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let go of me!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:19.52,0:48:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This fire should notify \Nthe surrounding villages of you too...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:25.61,0:48:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't attack villages...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:29.19,0:48:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:32.15,0:48:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally able to move to the Inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:35.95,0:48:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as long as I don't spread the curse...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:44.08,0:48:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:52.76,0:48:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:53.80,0:48:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I haven't touched you yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:48:58.72,0:48:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:01.81,0:49:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:04.94,0:49:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:08.19,0:49:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,have I done?
Dialogue: 10,0:49:18.24,0:49:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can no longer \Nuse that soul.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:22.62,0:49:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All I wanted was to help Shiva...
Dialogue: 10,0:49:33.09,0:49:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somewhere \Nthat I want you to take me.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:39.56,0:49:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:26.10,0:50:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva, you brought this for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:16.42,0:52:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:40.32,0:52:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay with her for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:03.44,0:54:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll head further down.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:08.91,0:54:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:11.24,0:54:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:44.69,0:54:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:46.28,0:54:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:00.83,0:55:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the closest.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:05.38,0:55:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home, Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:08.97,0:55:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a soul, \Nbut we'll return this.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:13.68,0:55:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a guest today.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:19.31,0:55:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear something.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:21.94,0:55:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:23.69,0:55:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mother's voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:25.90,0:55:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a sound than a voice.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:28.61,0:55:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be described as words. \NIt's like a song.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:38.87,0:55:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, speak to Mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:48.47,0:55:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:52.80,0:55:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:55.60,0:55:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:58.06,0:56:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell us how to break her curse.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:04.23,0:56:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do anything I can do to help!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:07.28,0:56:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my light...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:14.20,0:56:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was always in the dark.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:18.95,0:56:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shiva wasn't there...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:21.87,0:56:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've been that way forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:24.96,0:56:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgetting my breath, my pulse, \Nmy sleep, and even myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:31.47,0:56:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want her to feel the pain \Nof losing everything!
Dialogue: 10,0:56:38.68,0:56:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:40.43,0:56:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left \Nthat I can do for her.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:46.40,0:56:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you please, save Shiva's soul.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:50.78,0:56:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If my voice is being heard...
Dialogue: 10,0:56:54.20,0:56:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,please break this curse.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:01.75,0:57:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva...
Dialogue: 10,0:57:07.00,0:57:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:57:10.92,0:57:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:25.90,0:57:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I only...
Dialogue: 10,0:57:31.65,0:57:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,wanted to stay beside you.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:45.71,0:57:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now? \NIt's just as Mother says.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:50.96,0:57:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You two should have known \Nwhat that meant for the both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:58.47,0:58:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Knew...
Dialogue: 10,0:58:01.06,0:58:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was an end to everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:08.86,0:58:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiva...
Dialogue: 10,0:58:10.94,0:58:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can ...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:58:14.82,0:58:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,only take from you and not give?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:49.08,0:59:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:59:56.09,0:59:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Teacher!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:58.55,0:59:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:59.84,1:00:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:02.05,1:00:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay by my side!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:06.10,1:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, all right.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:22.03,1:00:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If even someone like me...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:25.37,1:00:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,can become your light.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:47.72,1:00:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:51.27,1:00:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I was having a dream.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:55.44,1:00:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A really scary dream.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:58.53,1:01:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It was dark and quiet, and it felt like \NI was going to be alone again...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:03.82,1:01:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll stay by your side.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:14.04,1:01:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:16.71,1:01:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I took it without asking...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:19.42,1:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you, Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:22.76,1:01:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I thought that I should \Nhold on to it carefully from now.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:27.51,1:01:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,1:01:28.43,1:01:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you open it?
Dialogue: 10,1:01:33.73,1:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shi...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:59.04,1:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, I'll walk.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:22.94,1:02:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:24.03,1:02:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:26.36,1:02:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:32.62,1:02:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shiva.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:56.56,1:02:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 10,1:02:58.69,1:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the long way back.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:01.06,1:03:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
